<example id="1" format="line_items">
<input>
A startup needs an internal web tool for sales pipeline management with role-based access and weekly reporting.
</input>
<output>
1. Discovery and requirements alignment - 12h - Product Manager
2. UX wireframes and UI design - 24h - Product Designer
3. Backend API for pipeline CRUD - 40h - Backend Engineer
4. Role-based authentication and authorization - 24h - Backend Engineer
5. Frontend dashboard and forms - 48h - Frontend Engineer
6. Weekly report generation and export - 20h - Backend Engineer
7. QA testing and bug fixing - 24h - QA Engineer
Total estimated hours: 192h
</output>
</example>

<example id="2" format="phases_table">
<input>
A company wants a mobile app MVP for appointment booking, reminders, and basic user profiles.
</input>
<output>
| Phase | Tasks | Hours | Team |
