| Discovery | Scope definition and acceptance criteria | 16 | PM + Tech Lead |
| Design | User flows and visual design | 28 | Product Designer |
| Backend | APIs for users, appointments, reminders | 52 | Backend Engineer |
| Mobile | Booking flow, profile, notifications | 72 | Mobile Engineer |
| QA | Functional testing and stabilization | 28 | QA Engineer |
| Total | - | 196 | Core team |
</output>
</example>
